  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOn contabo-12, Heap is >3GB, the heapsnapshot file taken was ~1.4GB, then Heap becomes ~9GB\r\n\r\n<img width=\"820\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-02-24 at 11 06 24\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/155685558-80c671a1-4b30-42c9-ba02-0cc09734efc7.png\">\r\n\r\nThe Heap Space Used metric is normal\r\n<img width=\"805\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-02-25 at 15 57 39\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/155685790-ee430b07-7932-44e8-8985-70ddcaf559c8.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nAfter taking a heap snapshot, heap memory should be smaller, normally 2G-2.5G",
